HEADWORD: Comptograph
<hw>Comp"to*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>compter</ets> to count + <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>A machine
for adding numbers and making a printed record of the sum. An older term
for an <er>adding machine</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Comptometer</ent>⟦br⟧
